and to see her through this process.

747
00:45:24.180 --> 00:45:25.306
Can you?

748
00:45:27.684 --> 00:45:29.561
That'll be all. Sam.

749
00:46:01.384 --> 00:46:03.803
Yeah. I'm in.

750
00:46:09.976 --> 00:46:12.187
