00:48:16.352 --> 00:48:18.563
♪ A perfect story ♪

782
00:48:18.646 --> 00:48:21.899
♪ If I hadn't fallen ♪

783
00:48:21.983 --> 00:48:25.445
♪ If my heart hadn't been broken ♪

784
00:48:25.528 --> 00:48:27.172
♪ If I didn't know pain.
I wouldn't know...

