00:48:27.196 --> 00:48:30.158
We agreed you'd be in disguise.

786
00:48:30.241 --> 00:48:32.452
I am in disguise.

787
00:48:32.535 --> 00:48:35.330
That hat is outrageous.

788
00:48:35.413 --> 00:48:38.875
